    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Add an Image\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to describe an image.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. The image you just looked at in the Unit Guide can be found in the **Library** when you click the button labeled **Add**. Attach it to your prompt.\r\n2. Prompt AI Chat to describe the image and list as many things as possible. *Can't come up with your own prompt? That's ok! You can copy one from below the instructions.*\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n4. Then read **AI Chat's response** and **compare** it to what **you listed** about the image **in your Unit Guide**.\r\n5. Complete the **\"What's in an image?\"** and **\"Privacy and Ethical Concerns\"** sections in your Unit Guide.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I add an image?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Add** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Library**\r\n- Then browse the existing images.\r\n- When you have an image to upload, click the checkbox next to it to select it and then click **Attach**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n>Describe this image. List as many things as you can notice in the image.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
